Instructions

In this experiment, you will read nine conversations between two speakers, as in this example, where Candy asks a question, and Lenny responds.

Candy: Is this house big?
Lenny: Cassandra suggested that it's huge.

We ask you to judge how well the response fits the question. You will give your judgment on a slider marked 'totally doesn't fit' at one end and 'totally fits' at the other.

The experiment will take around 2 minutes, and you will be paid 40 cents.

By clicking on the button below, you agree to participate in this experiment, which is conducted by researchers at the University of Stuttgart. You may withdraw from this experiment at any time. The data collected will be anonymous and confidential. If you have any questions, you may contact the requester through Prolific's platform, or directly at st180735@stud.uni-stuttgart.de.
